'''陈旭然'''（{{bd|1968年|8月21日|1998年|12月30日}}），原[[广东电视台|广东电视台]]女节目主持人、制片人，[[太平洋影音公司|太平洋影音公司]]签约歌手。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmw.cn/01shsb/1999-01/16/GB/861%5ESH12-111.htm |title=解读陈旭然 |accessdate=2014-09-10 |archive-date=2014-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910195146/http://www.gmw.cn/01shsb/1999-01/16/GB/861%5ESH12-111.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>[http://week-hzrb.hangzhou.com.cn/system/2009/09/01/010163011.shtml 陈旭然照片《摄影演变30年》] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140910200229/http://week-hzrb.hangzhou.com.cn/system/2009/09/01/010163011.shtml |date=2014-09-10 }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gmw.cn/01shsb/1999-01/16/GB/861%5eSH12-104.htm |title=陈旭然被杀之谜 |accessdate=2014-05-16 |archive-date=2014-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517163525/http://www.gmw.cn/01shsb/1999-01/16/GB/861%5eSH12-104.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.show160.com/news/new-671.html |title=广东主持人陈旭然被害案揭秘 |access-date=2014-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517130621/http://www.show160.com/news/new-671.html |archive-date=2014-05-17 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.ifeng.com/society/1/200909/0901_343_1328722.shtml |title=广东电视台主持人陈旭然被害 警方引蛇出洞 |accessdate=2014-05-16 |archive-date=2014-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517153826/http://news.ifeng.com/society/1/200909/0901_343_1328722.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://news.21cn.com/zhuanti/social/tanjing/dongtai/2008/04/21/4624554.shtml |title=陈旭然之死疑点重重 |access-date=2014-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304201332/http://news.21cn.com/zhuanti/social/tanjing/dongtai/2008/04/21/4624554.shtml |archive-date=2016-03-04 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/m/28616.html |title=死后身价反而“暴涨” 主持人陈旭然成摇钱树 |accessdate=2014-05-16 |archive-date=2014-05-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140517152141/http://ent.sina.com.cn/s/m/28616.html |dead-url=no }}